Q/N$, our result\nimplies indeed that symbol matched filtering is not capacity achieving at high\nSNR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 May 2014 10:15:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Aug 2014 08:26:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-05"}
