sk region, which can generate a\npositive metallicity gradient, and the subsequent chemical evolution of the\ndisk, which results in a flattening effect of a metallicity gradient at later\nepochs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 May 2014 14:03:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
